ivacy</a></h3>\n  <div class=\"topic-category\">\n      <span class=\"badge-wrapper bullet\">\n        <span class=\"badge-category-bg\" style=\"background-color: #F7941D;\"></span>\n        <span class=\"badge-category clear-badge\">\n          <span class=\"category-name\">Implementation</span>\n        </span>\n      </span>\n    <div class=\"topic-header-extra\">\n      <div class=\"list-tags\">\n        <div class=\"discourse-tags\">\n          <svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-tag svg-icon svg-string\"><use href=\"#tag\"></use></svg>\n            <span class=\"discourse-tag simple\">privacy</span>\n            <span class=\"discourse-tag simple\">wallet</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n  <p>I had built a tool for spoofing wallet fingerprint in 2023 which could be improved further to fix wallet fingerprinting: https://gitlab.com/1440000bytes/goldfish</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n</details>",
